## Hardware Designs

Hardware designs, schematics, and mechanical drawings in this repository are licensed under the CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S v2).

You may redistribute and modify these designs under the terms of the CERN-OHL-S v2. A copy of the licence is available at https://cern-ohl.web.cern.ch/

The hardware designs are provided "as-is" without any warranty. Users are responsible for ensuring safety and compliance with local electrical codes and regulations when building and installing the hardware.

